<p>Yes, and it is done, with permission from Zyn and working with Smapti.</p>
<p>As stated in the article, SCP-173 is a secondary use of the image of the art piece &quot;Untitled 2004&quot;, which was created by Izumi Kato. The concept of SCP-173 does not have any relationship with the artist's original concept of &quot;Untitled 2004&quot;.</p>
<p><strong>Images of the &quot;Untitled 2004&quot; sculpture may be used for non-commercial purposes only.</strong></p>

